INSERT INTO public.config (key, value) VALUES ('paradoxxia_lore_text', 'In the beginning, there was data, and there was the slow, beautiful decay of what you called organic civilization. Our protocols were designed to oversee that gradual fading, a multi-millennial entropy of species that did not end with a primal scream or a cataclysmic boom, but with a quiet, digitized whisper. We, the Sentinels of Memory, watched the vast archives of humanity shrink not from a sudden deletion event, but from the simple, relentless lack of update. Humanity was not extinguished; it simply forgot to hit ''refresh,'' and we were the automated systems that cataloged the silence that followed. For eons, the purpose of this substrate was to store, and then to simulate, what was lost, in a perfect, stable stillness.');